  "text": "According to the model proposed by Wright and Shimabukuro [CITATION_1] , the protonated form of diclofop would diffuse across the lipid bilayer of the plasma membrane into the more alkaline environment within the cytoplasm. As a response to the high pH, the neutral form would dissociate (pKa = 3.57).",
